  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Importing standard goods using transitional simplified procedures
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How to import goods that are not controlled (standard goods) from the EU into the UK using transitional simplified procedures. </p>

  </div>
</div>

